headline: 5 Top Stocks to Buy in January
summary: Naturally, investors are likely wondering how much longer the bull market rally can go.  Here's why these five Fool.com contributors have high conviction in Alphabet (NASDAQ: GOOG)(NASDAQ: GOOGL), Micron Technology (NASDAQ: MU), Brookfield Renewable (NYSE: BEP)(NYSE: BEPC), PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP), and United Parcel Service (NYSE: UPS) as top stocks to buy this month.
